The columns that I found interesting are 
1) Wildlife Species because specific species like Canada goose and unknown bird - large have high cost repairs and have high volume of records.
2) Wildlife_size because cost_repair is increasing with increasing wildlife size.
3) Effect_Amount_of_damage because substantial damages have high cost repairs and the remaining have low.
4) Aircraft_Airline_Operator because specific operators have high costs.
5) Aircraft_Make_Model because specific models have high repair costs.
